        "id": "writing-guide",
        "title": "Writing Guide",
        "scrollable": true,
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "heading",
            "level": 1,
            "text": "Whales – Guardians of the Climate",
            "className": "text-4xl font-bold text-indigo-700 text-center"
          },
          {
            "type": "heading",
            "level": 1,
            "text": "Lesson 7: Writing Guide",
            "className": "text-4xl font-bold text-indigo-700 mb-6 text-center"
          },

          {
            "type": "heading",
            "level": 3,
            "text": "GUIDE TO WRITING A LETTER TO JAPANESE PEOPLE TO PROTECT WHALES",
            "className": "text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600"
          },

          {
            "type": "heading",
            "level": 4,
            "text": "1. Opening",
            "className": "text-xl font-semibold text-blue-600 pt-2"
          },
          {
            "type": "heading",
            "level": 5,
            "text": "Instructions:",
            "className": "text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 pt-1"
          },
          {
            "type": "list",
            "ordered": true,
            "items": [
              "Start with a formal greeting",
              "Introduce yourself (if needed)",
              "Politely state the purpose of your letter"
            ],
            "className": "list-decimal list-inside ml-6 space-y-1"
          },
          {
            "type": "heading",
            "level": 5,
            "text": "Examples:",
            "className": "text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 pt-1 mt-4"
          },
          {
            "type": "list",
            "ordered": false,
            "items": [
              "Dear Japanese people,",
              "I am a student from Vietnam, ... ",
              "I am writing to express my concerns about..."
            ],
            "className": "list-disc list-inside ml-6 space-y-1 text-gray-700"
          },

          {
            "type": "heading",
            "level": 4,
            "text": "2. Main Content",
            "className": "text-xl font-semibold text-blue-600 pt-2 mt-4"
          },

          {
            "type": "heading",
            "level": 5,
            "text": "2.1. Show Understanding",
            "className": "text-lg font-semibold text-blue-600 pt-2"
          },
          {
            "type": "heading",
            "level": 6,
            "text": "Instructions:",
            "className": "text-md font-semibold text-gray-700 pt-1"
          },
          {
            "type": "list",
            "ordered": false,
            "items": [
              "Acknowledge cultural value",
              "Show respect for tradition"
            ],
            "className": "list-disc list-inside ml-6 space-y-1"
          },
          {
            "type": "heading",
            "level": 6,
            "text": "Examples:",
            "className": "text-md font-semibold text-gray-700 pt-1 mt-2"
          },
          {
            "type": "list",
            "ordered": false,
            "items": [
              "I understand that whaling has been part of Japanese tradition for centuries...",
              "We deeply respect Japan's rich maritime heritage and cultural practices..."
            ],
            "className": "list-disc list-inside ml-6 space-y-1 text-gray-700"
          },

          {
            "type": "heading",
            "level": 5,
            "text": "2.2. Present the Issue",
            "className": "text-lg font-semibold text-blue-600 pt-2"
          },
          {
            "type": "heading",
            "level": 6,
            "text": "Instructions:",
            "className": "text-md font-semibold text-gray-700 pt-1"
          },
          {
            "type": "list",
            "ordered": false,
            "items": [
              "Discuss the danger to whale species",
              "Explain the ecological impact",
              "Highlight environmental importance"
            ],
            "className": "list-disc list-inside ml-6 space-y-1"
          },
          {
            "type": "heading",
            "level": 6,
            "text": "Examples:",
            "className": "text-md font-semibold text-gray-700 pt-1 mt-2"
          },
          {
            "type": "list",
            "ordered": false,
            "items": [
              "Many whale species are now endangered, with some populations reduced to just a few hundred individuals...",
              "The decline of whale populations disrupts the ocean's delicate ecosystem balance...",
              "Whales play a crucial role in carbon sequestration, helping to combat climate change..."
            ],
            "className": "list-disc list-inside ml-6 space-y-1 text-gray-700"
          },

          {
            "type": "heading",
            "level": 5,
            "text": "2.3. Propose Solutions",
            "className": "text-lg font-semibold text-blue-600 pt-2"
          },
          {
            "type": "heading",
            "level": 6,
            "text": "Instructions:",
            "className": "text-md font-semibold text-gray-700 pt-1"
          },
          {
            "type": "list",
            "ordered": false,
            "items": [
              "Suggest alternative food sources",
              "Propose sustainable tourism options",
              "Encourage international cooperation"
            ],
            "className": "list-disc list-inside ml-6 space-y-1"
          },
          {
            "type": "heading",
            "level": 6,
            "text": "Examples:",
            "className": "text-md font-semibold text-gray-700 pt-1 mt-2"
          },
          {
            "type": "list",
            "ordered": false,
            "items": [
              "There are many sustainable seafood options that can provide similar nutritional benefits...",
              "Whale watching offers a sustainable economic alternative that can benefit coastal communities...",
              "By working together on conservation efforts, we can protect these magnificent creatures for future generations..."
            ],
            "className": "list-disc list-inside ml-6 space-y-1 text-gray-700"
          },

          {
            "type": "heading",
            "level": 4,
            "text": "3. Letter Closing",
            "className": "text-xl font-semibold text-blue-600 pt-2 mt-4"
          },
          {
            "type": "heading",
            "level": 5,
            "text": "Instructions:",
            "className": "text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 pt-1"
          },
          {
            "type": "list",
            "ordered": true,
            "items": [
              "Summarize your key message",
              "Express hope for positive change",
              "Thank the reader and sign off"
            ],
            "className": "list-decimal list-inside ml-6 space-y-1"
          },
          {
            "type": "heading",
            "level": 5,
            "text": "Examples:",
            "className": "text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 pt-1 mt-2"
          },
          {
            "type": "list",
            "ordered": false,
            "items": [
              "In conclusion, protecting whales is not just about conservation—it's about preserving the health of our entire planet.",
              "I sincerely hope you will consider these points and join the global effort to protect these magnificent creatures.",
              "Thank you for taking the time to consider this important matter. Sincerely, [Your Name]"
            ],
            "className": "list-disc list-inside ml-6 space-y-1 text-gray-700"
          },

          {
            "type": "heading",
            "level": 4,
            "text": "4. Useful Phrases",
            "className": "text-xl font-semibold text-blue-600 pt-2 mt-4"
          },
          {
            "type": "table",
            "headers": ["Purpose", "Example Phrase"],
            "rows": [
              [
                "Opening",
                "I am writing to express my concerns about... / I would like to bring to your attention..."
              ],
              [
                "Acknowledgment",
                "I understand that... / We appreciate that... / It's important to recognize that..."
              ],
              [
                "Presenting the issue",
                "However, it's concerning that... / Unfortunately, the current situation... / Research shows that..."
              ],
              [
                "Proposing solutions",
                "I would like to suggest... / An alternative approach could be... / We could work together to..."
              ],
              [
                "Closing",
                "I believe that by working together... / I hope you will consider... / Thank you for your attention to this important matter."
              ]
            ],
            "className": "w-full border-collapse mt-2"
          },

          {
            "type": "heading",
            "level": 4,
            "text": "5. Writing Tips",
            "className": "text-xl font-semibold text-blue-600 pt-2 mt-4"
          },
          {
            "type": "list",
            "ordered": false,
            "items": [
              "Be respectful and polite in tone",
              "Use facts and statistics to support your points",
              "Show empathy and understanding of cultural perspectives",
              "Keep your message concise and focused",
              "End with a clear call to action"
            ],
            "className": "list-disc list-inside ml-6 space-y-1"
          },
          {
            "type": "heading",
            "level": 5,
            "text": "Examples of Good vs. Poor Phrasing:",
            "className": "text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 pt-1 mt-2"
          },
          {
            "type": "list",
            "ordered": false,
            "items": [
              "Better: 'I hope you'll consider...' (instead of 'You must...')",
              "Better: 'Research shows that whale populations have declined by X%...' (instead of 'Everyone knows that...')",
              "Better: 'I understand the cultural significance, and I believe we can find solutions...' (instead of 'Your traditions are wrong...')",
              "Better: 'I'll be brief in outlining three key points...' (instead of 'There are many things to say about this...')",
              "Better: 'I encourage you to support policies that protect marine life...' (instead of 'You need to do something about this...')"
            ],
            "className": "list-disc list-inside ml-6 space-y-1 text-gray-700"
          }
        ],
        "containerClassName": "bg-white bg-opacity-90 rounded-xl p-10 shadow-2xl text-xl"
      }
    ]
  }
